<br>
For the first event, however, I suggest a combination swap meet/fledgling meet and greet.  I've got a TON of stuff in the bank that I've been saving for &quot;newbies&quot; -- without realizing that my own guildmembers could use some of it too!  Doh!<br>
<br>
And there are plenty of new people I've never met, that I want to meet. I can't wait!<br>
<br>
Where can we have it where we won't be constantly interrupted, and where all members can go?  The only place I can think of is the tunnel in East Commons -- guys, help me out if you can think of a better spot.<br>
<br>
